<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/20906539" target="_blank" data-id="543105" data-za-element-name="Title">
做为初入职的Web前端开发，应该如何尽快提高自己的能力？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/20906539/answer/132338059">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="48454056">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="132338059"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>103</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
