<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/49043143" target="_blank" data-id="11833054" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何实现 Babel 编译器？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/49043143/answer/113970082">
