<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/40035517" target="_blank" data-id="8221619" data-za-element-name="Title">
前端如何更好的实现接口的缓存和更新?
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/40035517/answer/84372581">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="29180124">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="84372581"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>102</a>
</div>

