<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/36350236" target="_blank" data-id="6747212" data-za-element-name="Title">
HTML5有哪些创意类型？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/36350236/answer/68597229">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="22858032">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="68597229"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>102</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
