<div class="feed-main">
<div class="content">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/28979908" target="_blank" data-id="3774921" data-za-element-name="Title">
怎么看 LinkedIn 放弃 Scala 和 Node.js？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/28979908/answer/44441451">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="13171377">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="44441451"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>102</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
