<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/35864634" target="_blank" data-id="6552589" data-za-element-name="Title">
前端学习几年后遇到瓶颈了，该怎么办？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/35864634/answer/64816225">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="21342147">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="64816225"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>101</a>
</div>

