<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/28565295" target="_blank" data-id="3609010" data-za-element-name="Title">
写这样一个求婚网页，需要具备什么IT技能？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/28565295/answer/41290243">
